Source: https://developer.garmin.com/connect-iq/core-topics/glances

This example shows how to use the ':glance' annotation in Monkey C to specify modules and classes required for Glance mode. This helps in managing memory usage by only including necessary components when the widget runs in a limited-memory glance environment.

```Monkey C
