### Implement Glance View in Monkey C

Source: https://developer.garmin.com/connect-iq/core-topics/glances

This snippet demonstrates how to implement a Glance View for your Connect IQ widget. It shows overriding the getGlanceView method to return a custom GlanceView implementation, which is crucial for displaying information in the glance list.

```Monkey C
using Toybox.WatchUi;

class MyGlanceView extends WatchUi.GlanceView {

    function initialize() {
        GlanceView.initialize();
    }

    function onUpdate() {
        // Update glance view content here
        return true;
    }

}

class MyApp extends AppBase {

    function initialize() {
        AppBase.initialize();
    }

    function getGlanceView() {
        return new MyGlanceView();
    }

}
```

